==English==

===Noun===
'''[[stat]] [[whore]]'''  (''plural:'' '''[[stat whores]]''')

# A [[Wiktionarian]] afflicted with [http://kohl.wikimedia.org/~kate/cgi-bin/count_edits?user=&dbname=enwiktionary editcountitis].
# A person that increases their statistics (especially in video-games) through unscrupulous means.

===Verb===
{{en-infl-reg-other-e|stat whor|e}}

# To guide one's actions based on the (usually public) statistic results those actions will generate.
#:''He's '''stat whoring''' by using Javascript on Wiktionary.''

